---

<BaseLayout
  title="Forex Trading Strategies 2026: Proven Methods for Beginners"
  description="Learn profitable forex trading strategies. From trend following to price action, discover which strategy fits your trading style. Complete guide with examples."
>
  <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
  <Breadcrumb slot="breadcrumb" items={[
    { text: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { text: 'Guides', href: '/guides/' },
    { text: 'Forex Strategy', current: true }
  ]} />

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="badge-icon">üìä</span>
          STRATEGY GUIDE
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Forex Trading Strategies</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          Proven strategies that work in real markets. Learn the rules, practice on demo, and find the approach that fits your style.
        </p>

        <!-- Key Stats -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
          {keyStats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="stat-card">
              <div class="stat-icon">{stat.icon}</div>
              <span class="stat-value">{stat.value}</span>
              <span class="stat-label">{stat.label}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ANCHOR NAVIGATION -->
  <nav class="anchor-nav" id="anchorNav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="anchor-links">
        {anchorMenuItems.map((item) => (
          <a href={item.href} class="anchor-link">{item.text}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- STRATEGIES SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="strategies">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Forex Trading Strategies</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Each strategy has clear rules for entry, exit, and risk management. Pick one that matches your personality and schedule.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="strategies-list">
        {strategies.map((strategy, index) => (
          <div class="strategy-card">
            <div class="strategy-header">
              <div class="strategy-number">{index + 1}</div>
              <div class="strategy-info">
                <h3 class="strategy-name">{strategy.name}</h3>
                <div class="strategy-meta">
                  <span class={`difficulty-badge ${strategy.difficulty.toLowerCase()}`}>{strategy.difficulty}</span>
                  <span class="timeframe-badge">{strategy.timeframe}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="strategy-description">{strategy.description}</p>

            <div class="strategy-details">
              <div class="how-to">
                <h4>How to Trade It:</h4>
                <ol>
                  {strategy.howTo.map((step) => (
                    <li>{step}</li>
                  ))}
                </ol>
              </div>

              <div class="strategy-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <span class="stat-label">Best Pairs</span>
                  <span class="stat-value">{strategy.bestPairs.join(', ')}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <span class="stat-label">Win Rate</span>
                  <span class="stat-value">{strategy.winRate}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <span class="stat-label">Risk/Reward</span>
                  <span class="stat-value">{strategy.riskReward}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STRATEGY COMPONENTS -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="components">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Every Strategy Needs These</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          A complete trading strategy isn't just about entries. These components turn a trading idea into a tradeable system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="components-grid">
        {strategyComponents.map((component) => (
          <div class="component-card">
            <span class="component-icon">{component.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="component-title">{component.title}</h3>
            <p class="component-description">{component.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO CHOOSE -->
  <section class="section" id="choose">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">How to Choose Your Strategy</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          The best strategy is one you can actually follow consistently. Match it to your lifestyle.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="choose-content">
        <div class="choose-grid">
          <div class="choose-card">
            <h4>If You Have a Full-Time Job...</h4>
            <p>Use 4H or Daily charts. Check charts morning and evening. Swing trading and trend following work well. Don't scalp or day trade - you'll miss signals and make mistakes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="choose-card">
            <h4>If You're Impatient...</h4>
            <p>Breakout trading or London Breakout gives quick results. Avoid daily timeframes - the wait will drive you crazy. Consider scalping if you can handle the intensity.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="choose-card">
            <h4>If You Like Analysis...</h4>
            <p>Price action or Fibonacci strategies let you dig into charts. You'll enjoy analyzing patterns and levels. Avoid simple MA crossovers - too mechanical.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="choose-card">
            <h4>If You Want Simplicity...</h4>
            <p>Support/Resistance or MA Crossover strategies have clear, simple rules. Avoid indicator-heavy strategies or complex pattern recognition.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-tip">
          <p><strong>The truth:</strong> No strategy is perfect. All have losing streaks. The best strategy is one you understand, trust, and can execute consistently when emotions run high.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BROKERS SECTION -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="brokers">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Best Brokers for Strategy Trading</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Brokers with good charting tools, educational resources, and reliable execution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="brokers-grid">
        {featuredBrokers.map((broker) => (
          <div class={`broker-card ${broker.featured ? 'featured' : ''}`}>
            {broker.featured && <span class="featured-badge">Top Pick</span>}
            <div class="broker-header">
              <img src={broker.logo} alt={`${broker.name} logo`} class="broker-logo" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="broker-rating">
                <span class="rating-stars">{'‚òÖ'.repeat(parseInt(broker.stars))}</span>
                <span class="rating-value">{broker.rating}/5</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="broker-name">{broker.name}</h3>
            <ul class="broker-features">
              {broker.features.map((feature) => (
                <li>{feature}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <a href={broker.ctaLink} class="broker-cta">{broker.ctaText}</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="section-cta">
        <a href="/brokers/" class="cta-button secondary">
          Compare All Brokers
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="faqs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Strategy FAQs</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Common questions about forex trading strategies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        {faqs.map((faq) => (
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-question">{faq.question}</summary>
            <p class="faq-answer">{faq.answer}</p>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="final-cta">
        <h2>Ready to Test These Strategies?</h2>
        <p>Open a demo account and practice with virtual money. Master one strategy before risking real capital.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/brokers/" class="cta-button primary">Find a Broker</a>
          <a href="/guides/forex-trading-basics/" class="cta-button secondary">Learn Forex Basics</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--charcoal) 0%, #2d3436 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    background: rgba(255, 72, 0, 0.2);
    color: var(--brand-orange);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .badge-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand-orange);
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* Anchor Navigation */
  .anchor-nav {
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }

  .anchor-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .anchor-link {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .anchor-link:hover {
    color: var(--brand-orange);
    background: rgba(255, 72, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Section Styles */
  .section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
  }

  .section-alt {
    background: var(--gray-50);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Strategies List */
  .strategies-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .strategy-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .strategy-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .strategy-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    min-width: 48px;
    background: var(--brand-orange);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .strategy-name {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
  }

  .strategy-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .difficulty-badge,
  .timeframe-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .difficulty-badge.beginner {
    background: #d1fae5;
    color: #065f46;
  }

  .difficulty-badge.intermediate {
    background: #fef3c7;
    color: #92400e;
  }

  .timeframe-badge {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .strategy-description {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .strategy-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .how-to h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .how-to ol {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .how-to li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .strategy-stats {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .strategy-stats .stat-item {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .strategy-stats .stat-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .strategy-stats .stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--gray-500);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

